#### System State Flow
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Phase2["Phase 2 (Complete)"]
        Adapters["Adapters<br/>(emit tool_call, tool_result, thinking)"]
    end

    subgraph Phase3["Phase 3 (This Phase)"]
        Route["Run Route<br/>broadcastAgentEvent()"]
