#### Sequence: Tool Call Event Flow (Complete Pipeline)
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Adapter as ClaudeCodeAdapter
    participant Route as /api/agents/run
    participant Storage as EventStorageService
    participant SSE as SSEManager
    participant Hook as useAgentSSE
    participant State as SessionState

    Adapter->>Route: onEvent({ type: 'tool_call', data: {...} })
    Route->>Storage: append(sessionId, event)
    Storage-->>Route: evt_001 (ID assigned)
    Route->>SSE: broadcast('agents', 'agent_tool_call', {..., sessionId})
    SSE-->>Hook: SSE event received
    Hook->>Hook: Parse agent_tool_call
    Hook->>State: onToolCall(toolName, input, toolCallId, sessionId)
    State->>State: Update session messages with contentType='tool_call'
```

#### Sequence: Event Fetch on Connect (Race Condition Handling)
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Component Mount
    participant Hook as useAgentSSE
    participant API as GET /events
    participant SSE as EventSource
    participant State as SessionState

    UI->>Hook: Mount hook
    Hook->>SSE: Connect EventSource
    Hook->>API: GET /events?sessionId=xxx
    API-->>Hook: [evt_001, evt_002, evt_003]
    Hook->>State: Apply events 001-003
    Note over Hook: Now listening for new events
    SSE-->>Hook: SSE: evt_004
    Hook->>Hook: Dedupe: 004 is new
    Hook->>State: Apply event 004
    SSE-->>Hook: SSE: evt_003 (duplicate)
    Hook->>Hook: Dedupe: 003 already seen, skip
```

