### Risks & Unknowns

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|
| SSE event ordering issues | MEDIUM | Event IDs provide ordering; client sorts by ID if needed |
| Memory leaks from listeners | MEDIUM | AbortController pattern in T012; mount/unmount test |
| Race between fetch and SSE | MEDIUM | Deduplicate by event ID; fetch completes before SSE processed |
| EventStorageService append() failure | LOW | **DYK-06 Decision**: Log warning with sessionId, continue with broadcast anyway. Users see event in real-time but may lose it on refresh. Storage failures are rare; UX prioritized over strict consistency. |
| Existing SSE behavior regression | HIGH | Run existing hook tests; verify text_delta still works |

